com.example.cheaptrip.handlers.converter.annotations

Annotation Type Json


  • @Target(value=METHOD)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface Json
    This is Used to Identify how to handle Retrofit Responses. The MultiConverterFactory takes care of converting them into JAVA-Objects by selecting the Converter Based on the Annotation. In this case (JSON): The Rest-API Response String (in format JSON) will be converted into a Java-Class holding all the Information.
